        <div class="field field-name-title field-type-ds field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even" property="dc:title"><h1 class="title">Portsmouth Listens</h1></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-pp-case-created field-type-ds field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><div class="submitted">First submitted by <a href="/en/people/plscully" title="View user profile." class="username" xml:lang="" about="/en/people/plscully" typeof="sioc:UserAccount" property="foaf:name" datatype="">Patrick L. Scully</a> on Mon, 01/18/2010 - 17:11</div></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-pp-case-changed field-type-ds field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><div class="submitted">Most recent changes by <a href="/en/people/plscully" title="View user profile." class="username" xml:lang="" about="/en/people/plscully" typeof="sioc:UserAccount" property="foaf:name" datatype="">Patrick L. Scully</a> on Mon, 02/01/2016 - 10:13</div></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-addthis field-type-addthis field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a class="addthis_button " addthis:title="Portsmouth Listens - Participedia" addthis:url="http://participedia.net/en/cases/portsmouth-listens-portsmouth-new-hampshire"><img src="http://s7.addthis.com/static/btn/sm-share-en.gif" alt="Share page with AddThis" />
