      <div class="field-group-format-wrapper" style="display: block;"><div class="field field-name-field-start-date field-type-date field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Start Date:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">[no data entered]</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-end-date field-type-date field-label-above"><div class="field-label">End Date:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">[no data entered]</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-ongoing field-type-list-boolean field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Ongoing:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">Yes</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-meeting-days-num field-type-number-decimal field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Number of Meeting Days:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">[no data entered]</div></div></div></div></div><div class="collapsible group-participants field-group-div speed-fast effect-none">
      <h3><span class="field-group-format-toggler">Participants</span></h3>
      <div class="field-group-format-wrapper" style="display: block;"><div class="field field-name-field-case-participant-count field-type-number-integer field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Total Number of Participants:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">850</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-demographics-target field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Targeted Participants (Demographics):&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_demographics_target%3A112">General Public</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-public-roles-target field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Targeted Participants (Public Roles):&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_public_roles_target%3A128">Lay Public</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_public_roles_target%3A129">Stakeholder Organizations (e.g. NGOs, Neighbourhood Associations, Industry Representatives)</a></div><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_public_roles_target%3A131">Elected Public Official</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_public_roles_target%3A132">Appointed Public Servants (e.g. Bureaucrats)</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-participant-selection field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Method of Recruitment:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_participant_selection%3A31">Open to all with targeted recruitment</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="collapsible group-process field-group-div speed-fast effect-none">
      <h3><span class="field-group-format-toggler">Process</span></h3>
      <div class="field-group-format-wrapper" style="display: block;"><div class="field field-name-field-methods field-type-node-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Methods:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/methods/deliberation">Deliberation</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/en/methods/study-circles">Study Circles</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-facilitated field-type-list-boolean field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Facilitation?:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">Yes</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-facilitation-type field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">If yes, were they ...:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_facilitation_type%3A171">Peer Facilitators (i.e. other participants not professional facilitators)</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-facilitation-method field-type-list-text field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Facetoface, Online or Both:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">Face-to-Face</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-communication-mode field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Type of Interaction among Participants:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_communication_mode%3A9">Discussion, Dialogue, or Deliberation</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_communication_mode%3A139">Informal Social Activities</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-decision-method field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Decision Method(s)?:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_decision_method%3A143">Getting sense of room/group (i.e. no formal voting)</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-decision-voting-type field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">If voting...:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">[no data entered]</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-decision-method-other field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Other: Decision Method:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">group priority setting; individual decisions to join ongoing work groups</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-targeted-audience field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Targeted Audience :&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_targeted_audience%3A151">General Public</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_targeted_audience%3A152">Elected Public Official</a></div><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_targeted_audience%3A153">Appointed Public Servants (e.g. bureaucrats)</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_targeted_audience%3A154">Organized Groups (e.g. NGOs, Business Associations)</a></div><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_targeted_audience%3A155">Media</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-audience-comm-method field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Method of Communication with Audience:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_audience_comm_method%3A157">Public Report</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_audience_comm_method%3A158">Policy Recommendations</a></div><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_audience_comm_method%3A159">Public Hearings/Meetings</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_audience_comm_method%3A160">Traditional Media (i.e. television, radio, newspapers)</a></div><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_audience_comm_method%3A161">New Media (i.e. internet, texting, etc)</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-audience-comm-method-other field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Other: Method of Communication with Audience:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">group priority setting; individual decisions to join ongoing work groups</div></div></div></div></div><div class="collapsible group-organizers field-group-div speed-fast effect-none">
      <h3><span class="field-group-format-toggler">Organizers</span></h3>
